nk?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1648246202123798%2Fposts%2F2439176316364112%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6Vmmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=fe2b6fbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1648246202123798/posts/2439176316364112?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"fc370cdf19d892f3c5d631068f710b19eb9a32e7","tid":1639671,"uid":125168,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"74b1004da388f2324bc13e2446554d5c371e689a","tid":1639671,"uid":247845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:43:13.000Z","msg":"有幾多部係呀sir爆?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:43:49.000Z","msg":"應該有一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a46eb3607d2172b8ce373bb2c11258fbe059f8bc","tid":1639671,"uid":33868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:44:25.000Z","msg":"閘大大餓咗咁多日應該肚餓了"},{"pid":"e1ae9890b8f8954de430896452c89844a7946df4","tid":1639671,"uid":36813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:45:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />港鐵應該多謝班popo OT 幫你換閘機"},{"pid":"d79a084f4d569d5895f382fa4ac20df3145b1bbc","tid":1639671,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:48:17.000Z","msg":"政府嘅陰謀：封網<br />\n<br />\n（分析+行動）政府有意部署封網，封網後香港變新疆！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639585</a><br />\n<br />\n星期二（10月8日）早上，港鐵就宣布提前在晚上八點停駛，點解政府未卜先知出現動亂？其實政府有心製造一個長期嘅亂局，然後用緊急法立更多惡法，其中最近葉國謙就話要準備封網，呢樣嘢可以對香港抗爭造成極嚴重打擊。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>斷網可毒啞香港人，新疆前車可鑑</ins></span></strong><br />\n斷網真係落實嘅話，<span style=\"color: red;\">最惡劣係好似新疆咁徹底斷網</span>，只有政府部門先可以上網，<span style=\"color: red;\">徹底封網的話，大家不但難以互通抗爭消息，而且香港訊息難以傳到海外，香港人也難以接收海外消息。西方人對香港嘅了解，只能經過政府嘅官方說法，或極少數流出嘅真相。</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">新疆早在2009年封網，同時限制境外人士到新疆旅遊，斷絕新疆對外聯繫，結果近年就出現新疆集中營。呢方面大家一定要警惕！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>大家不能掉以輕心</strong><br />\n或者有人認為政府會顧及香港嘅國際環境唔會輕易斷網，但現在中共已經失去理性，當中央黔驢技窮，損害香港利益而徹底封網並非不可。就好似半年前大家都唸唔到香港已經失去遊行以及戴口罩嘅自由。<br />\n<br />\n本文為節錄，全文請到此瀏覽：<br />\n<br />\n（分析+行動）政府有意部署封網，封網後香港變新疆！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639585</a>"},{"pid":"94011eb4ccd9db09a44fe019d7a68be386cdc7ad","tid":1639671,"uid":274906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:49:36.000Z","msg":"全撚部都係狗做嘅"},{"pid":"0efae5a8364b0cc2f6fabb30634f55c28868043c","tid":1639671,"uid":64962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:50:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52a999922fcfa01589b3e01edcb3b5d2cfcc1510","tid":1639671,"uid":331168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:50:28.000Z","msg":"全部都係黑警整爛"},{"pid":"ff45832d9b452bfe7663d857a6f89f0fa5d17de2","tid":1639671,"uid":22436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:52:57.000Z","msg":"班狗全日封站個陣又燒又搞爛左幾撚多?"},{"pid":"a2bfaa3a410ffe32a79ce1fabcffefa59857b97d","tid":1639671,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:55:55.000Z","msg":"瘋狂下載分享阿sir英姿<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/o0ouf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fo0ouf&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6Vmmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=6027fcf1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/o0ouf</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/eps58\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Feps58&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6Vmmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=0341c18d\" data-auto-