站出入口的捲閘維修人員亦復修及加固。<br />\n<br />\n在旺角站，客務中心玻璃窗被打碎，已經圍封起分隔付費區及非付費區，玻璃圍欄只餘下支架，港鐵以膠帶圍封，又以膠套封起損壞的售票機。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵周二仍然關閉十一個站，當中包括旺角及觀塘站。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">大家唔好唔記得除左拆鐵之外，日常仲可以繼續餵閘大大食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T23:46:59.000Z","msg":"好多都係警察打爛 <br />\n封完站都仲可以有人係入面打野"},{"pid":"40e8d642096a01589790f851430ea823b904984a","tid":1639671,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T23:54:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c3f7cded0a4f1fd3d9c2aa1dd9a8c462e5a9e02","tid":1639671,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6eca177f34499717de0b1e8e887a918e0f65c559","tid":1639671,"uid":250979,"like":5,"dislike":18,"score":-13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:33:25.000Z","msg":"全撚部齊頭數，on99<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T23:55:44.000Z","msg":"約數齊頭好正常"},{"pid":"be7a0c005f3fb9bfb128c25c994c2a40ff0154d2","tid":1639671,"uid":117301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T23:59:55.000Z","msg":"未又係POPO做<br />\n我發現只要係關左既站影到黑衣popo或者入邊冇壞野<br />\n<br />\n果個站都會極速開返 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家行過都影下入邊啦"},{"pid":"e9e31f021157f4f114713f8b09e242dce87cc3cc","tid":1639671,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:01:54.000Z","msg":"阿sir繼續加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f66e938ba564f32cd9db73a17a8e289aeeeafd8","tid":1639671,"uid":53695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:34:03.000Z","msg":"爆得嗰少少點屈啲年輕人呀，全線同我打爆佢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />This is an order<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3036f5a1